OL,3,C100-year-old veteran speaks of sadness
OL,4,Cof comrades he lost
OL,6,FIn the build up to Remembrance Day, a
OL,7,F100-year-old D-Day veteran from
OL,8,FLancaster has shared his journey from
OL,9,Fstorming the beaches of Normandy to
OL,10,Fbeing one of the first British
OL,11,Fsoldiers to witness the horrors of a
OL,12,FNazi concentration camp.
OL,14,FRichard Brock, a former East
OL,15,FLancashire Regiment soldier was 20
OL,16,Fyears old when he made the trip from
OL,17,Fhis home in Lancashire to Portsmouth
OL,18,Ffor the D-Day assault.
