OL,3,C100-year-old veteran speaks of sadness
OL,4,Cof comrades he lost
OL,6,FIn the battles that followed, all but
OL,7,F19 of the 130 men in Mr Brock's
OL,8,Fcompany were killed.
OL,10,FRichard was part of a handful of North
OL,11,FWest veterans who returned to Normandy
OL,12,Fthis summer for the 80th anniversary
OL,13,Fof D-Day.
OL,15,FIt was to mark Operation Overlord
OL,16,Fwhich took place on June 6th, 1944.
OL,18,FMore recently, Richard was a guest of
OL,19,Fhonour at the Sandbag Cafe for armed
OL,20,Fforces veterans in St George's Church
OL,21,Fin Preston.
