OL,3,C100-year-old veteran speaks of sadness
OL,4,Cof comrades he lost
OL,6,F"They have to know what happened
OL,7,Fbecause if it wasn't for the heroes,
OL,8,Fthe lads who passed on in Normandy,
OL,9,Flife would have been different here
OL,10,Ftoday."
OL,12,FRichard is believed to be the last
OL,13,Fsurviving member of his battalion.
OL,15,FSpeaking in June, he said: "I don't
OL,16,Fthink you're proud, you're just sad
OL,17,Ffor your pals that you've missed.
OL,19,F"All your mates were getting knocked
OL,20,Foff. I think I'm the last one.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
